description: Creates the specified tags for the specified WorkSpaces resource.

parameters.name: ResourceId
parameters.description: The identifier of the WorkSpaces resource. The supported resource types are WorkSpaces, registered directories, images, custom bundles, IP access control groups, and connection aliases.

parameters.name: Tags
parameters.description: The tags. Each WorkSpaces resource can have a maximum of 50 tags. (dict) --- Describes a tag. The key of the tag. Value (string) --- The value of the tag.
